Group Samples
================

This section contains information about samples as used within the Metasys API

### Get Network Device Attributes With Samples [GET /networkDevices/{id}/trendedAttributes]
Retrieves a collection of attributes under the specified network device for which samples are available.

+ Parameters
    + id (string) - The identifier of the network device

+ Request
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [token]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.metasysapi.v2+json)

    + Attributes
        + Include NetworkDeviceAttributeWithSamplesCollection
        + self:`https://{hostname}/api/v2/networkDevices/{id}/trendedAttributes` - A link to this collection

### Get Samples For A Network Device Attribute [GET /networkDevices/{id}/trendedAttributes/{attributeId}/samples{?startTime,endTime,page,pageSize,sort}]
Retrieves a collection of samples for the specified network device attribute during a particular date and time range.

Note that the parent endpoint `https://{hostname}/api/v2/networkDevices/{id}/trendedAttributes/{attributeId}` is not currently implemented.

+ Parameters
    + id (string) - The identifier of the network device
    + attributeId (number) - The identifier of the attribute for which to retrieve sample information
        + See /networkDevices/{id}/trendedAttributes for possible values
    + startTime (string) - The dateTime representing the earliest sample to return
    + endTime (string) - The dateTime representing the latest sample to return
    + page (number, optional) - The page number of items to return
        + Default: `1`
    + pageSize (number, optional) - The maximum number of items to return in the response. Valid range is 1-10,000.
        + Default: `1000`
    + sort (string, optional) - The criteria to use when sorting results (see [rules](#sorting-rules))
        + Accepted Values: `timestamp`
        + Default: `timestamp`

+ Request Analog Samples
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [token]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.metasysapi.v2+json)

    + Attributes(NetworkDeviceValueSamplesEntity)
      - items (array)
          - (ValueSampleAnalog)

+ Request Digital Samples
    + Headers

            Authorization: Bearer [token]

+ Response 200 (application/vnd.metasysapi.v2+json)

    + Attributes (NetworkDeviceValueSamplesEntity)
      - items (array)
          - (ValueSampleDigital)

